OMUNYE wabasolwa ecaleni lokubulawa kukaNksz Hillary Gardee, kulindeleke ukuthi avele eNkantolo yeMantshi yaseNelspruit, kusasa. USipho Mkhatshwa ushaye ingwijikhwebu, wathi yena useyafuna ukufaka isicelo sebheyili. Lokhu kulandela ukuthi yena nozakwabo ababili kuleli cala, oPhilemon Lukhele noMduduzi Gama, babethe abafuni ukufaka isicelo sebheyili ngesikhathi bevela enkantolo ngasekuqaleni kwenyanga. Ngaleso sikhathi, umbuso nawo wawuzwakalise ukuthi bobathathu abasolwa bangalinge banikwe ibheyili uma kwenzeka beyifuna, ukubuka ubukhulu becala. Akukacaci ukuthi umbuso uzoqhubeka yini nokuma emagameni awo okuthi kubo bobathathu abasolwa, akekho ofanelwe ukunikwa ibheyili uma esevela uMkhatshwa kusasa. Phambilini, kuvele ukuthi uMkhatshwa akusikho okokuqala ephambana nengalo yomthetho ngecala likaNksz Gardee. Ngaphambi kokuboshwa kwakhe, uSipho wanikwa incwadi yesivimbelo ngenxa yokuziphatha kwakhe okunodlame. I-EFF ngesitatimende, iveze ukuthi ubuholi bayo buzowuphelezela umndeni ukuya enkantolo ukutshengisa ukuzwelana nawo, ikakhulukazi uyise kaNksz Gardee obengunobhala-jikelele weqembu, uMnuz Godrich Gardee. USipho Lawrence Mkhatshwa, uMduduzi Gama noLukhele, babhekene necala lokubulala, elokudlwengula, elokubopha itulo lokubulala, elokuthumba nelokutholakala nesibhamu esingekho emthethweni. UNksz Gardee wabikwa njengomuntu odukile ngoLwesihlanu, ngo-Ephreli 29. Ngaleso sikhathi kwathiwa ugcine ukubonakala esezitolo eMbombela, ngezithuba zawo-5:30 ntambama. Idlanzana labantu ababezihambela, bebheke emsebenzini, yilo elathola isidumbu sakhe ngoLwesibili, ngoMeyi 3, ebangeni elilinganiselwa kumakhilomitha angu-40 ngaphandle kweMbombela. Umphumela wokuhlolwa kwesidumbu uveze ukuthi uGardee wadutshulwa ngemumva ekhanda, waphinde wagwazwa amanxeba amaningi emzimbeni. Imbangela yokubulawa kwakhe ayikakaziwa. 